This paper is about unsupervised representation learning, which is a topic that spans multiple sub-fields in computer science. However, given that the paper focuses on a specific technique (CURL) and presents theoretical results, it is most likely to be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, since the paper uses image datasets and discusses applications in natural language processing, it could also be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision) or cs.CL (Computation and Language). Finally, since the paper proposes a new algorithm, it could also be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
